title: Encyclopedia of Computational Mechanics (3 Volume Set)
description:
Encyclopedia of Computational Mechanics (3 Volume Set)(Wiley).pdf

Review:
"This three volume set provides the most comprehensive and up-to-date collection of knowledge about this increasingly important area of engineering science. The Encyclopedia provides a well-rounded and practical knowledge base that will serve as a foundation for the reader's research and practice in developing designs and in understanding, assessing and managing numerical analysis systems." (Zentralblatt MATH, 2010)
